Killa, you can use a proxy like Anonymizer and then download with Opera. I got letters a while back for some games and thats what I ended up doing. Opera is the only browser I know that has a torrent client built in. Other than that you can wait for FXG or other well known dvd rippers. Most companies don't search for dl'ing once they release the dvd. Why the US has to wait months behind the world to get dvd's, I don't know.
